{"tid":1944617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"越南暫停簽所有新出口大米合約 越南米佔香港大米4分1 商會稱影響不大","createTime":"2020-03-26T13:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T19:00:05.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2798f63340f6c5bb4ff98fdf13f63a5fc0d0bc","tid":1944617,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516912-20200326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516912-20200326.htm&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=43645d88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516912-20200326.htm&h=e1b79903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516912-20200326.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有本港米商表示，從越南在香港商務專員及出口商會了解，越南方面正檢視大米出口情況，暫時不與外地簽署大米出口合約，但認為只屬疫情保險措施，加上本港有足夠大米儲存及泰國大米出口正常，呼籲巿民不要搶購大米。<br />\n<br />\n香港米行商會理事長陳建年在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，前日一度聽到越南停止出口大米消息，其後向越南香港的商務專員及出口商會等了解，得悉晚上暫時撤回決定，不過當局將檢視出口情況，暫停簽出口合約，但不影響之前簽訂的合約，這幾天會續有大米出口。陳建年認為，大致不會有問題，因為上月的「搶米潮」，本港各入口商本月已購入更多大米，越南在本港入口大約佔25%，主要還是來自泰國，前日他們已經向泰國官方了解，得悉泰國如常出口大米，認為巿民不需搶米，重申香港有受政府監管的儲糧制度，不要引起不必要恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n他提到以往未有越南米入口時，香港曾經有9成大米來自泰國，認為如果越南暫停出口，泰國可以增加於香港巿場佔有率，又提到泰國是全球大米第二最大出口國，出口香港的只是小量。他說，越南與泰國的大米收成都沒有問題，事件或會令價格浮動，但大米價格主要是國際巿場主導。"},{"pid":"0b3671aef637292be4588d771925d9da95a5aaa6","tid":1944617,"uid":283222,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"米就唔洗搶，遲下會貴D啫，泰國遲下都會跟，連鎖效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f379082f934aa65a758e277d8547ef368ba66027","tid":1944617,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b118d2f17afe08aa694c27623143bddaa623e5c1","tid":1944617,"uid":107790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"香港有<span style=\"color: red;\">受政府監管的儲糧制度</span>，不要引起不必要恐慌<br />\n<br />\n唔講呢句都冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7215193b0befe2e798bf1910f0dab8f81ae35991","tid":1944617,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b118d2f17afe08aa694c27623143bddaa623e5c1","tid":1944617,"uid":107790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"香港有<span style=\"color: red;\">受政府監管的儲糧制度</span>，不要引起不必要恐慌<br />\n<br />\n唔講呢句都冇咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"屌笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}